{"tid":2078842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國潮牌Superdry退出中國市場 7月起陸續關閉門市","createTime":"2020-06-25T10:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T14:25:27.000Z","uid":28114,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1ea45ad6581ae41fc3b11507d9fb992d39fdcb","tid":2078842,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2020/06/25/phpTkfpW8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F06%2F25%2FphpTkfpW8.jpg&h=ce0c8fc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國潮牌極度乾燥（Superdry）宣布退出中國市場。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕在武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒疾病，COVID-19）疫情打擊下，英國潮牌極度乾燥（Superdry）宣布退出中國市場，自7月起將陸續關閉在中國的直營和授權門市，未來中國消費者將透過英國官網購買。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，Superdry本月18日指稱，已和在中國的合資夥伴赫基集團（Trendy International Group ）友好協商，決定結束4年合資關係。2家公司均表示，疫情的影響加速了終止合資企業的決定。<br />\n<br />\nSuperdry昨（24）日透過中國社群軟體微信的官方帳號表示，7月起將陸續關閉在中國的自營店及品牌電商旗艦店，未來將透過英國官網運營。目前，Superdry在中國共有25間直營店和41間授權門市，預計8月底前將關閉所有中國直營店，而授權門市將在今年底結束。<br />\n<br />\nSuperdry自2016年進入中國市場，2017年的業績還非常強勁，當期財年的收入年增長27.4％至7.520億英鎊。截至4月27日的2019財年內，Superdry收入和上一財年基本持平，毛利率和稅前利潤均下跌50％以上。<br />\n<br />\n據Superdry最新業績報告指出，疫情破壞業務和供應鏈，徹底打亂Superdry在中國市場的佈局。Superdry首席執行官Julian Dunkerton表示，從長遠來看，中國為Superdry帶來了巨大的機會，而隨着消費者的購物方式變化，公司將重點轉移到在線和批發等渠道，將重新定位在該地區的業務，以為Superdry帶來可盈利的未來增長的正確時機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3208674\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3208674&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=ea2e1e62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3208674&h=48a2a8d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3208674</a>"},{"pid":"cca7e73f59f845d57b0484d922219d4445f53e97","tid":2078842,"uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:50:00.000Z","msg":"香港執唔執？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8698c572bd1af00a00097ddc512ffa3bacfa4108","tid":2078842,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cca7e73f59f845d57b0484d922219d4445f53e97","tid":2078842,"uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:50:00.000Z","msg":"香港執唔執？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:50:42.000Z","msg":"又唔係特別好着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58644f0dd670d18005692ab0f1b811f4af896576","tid":2078842,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8698c572bd1af00a00097ddc512ffa3bacfa4108","tid":2078842,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cca7e73f59f845d57b0484d922219d4445f53e97","tid":2078842,"uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:50:00.000Z","msg":"香港執唔執？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:50:42.000Z","msg":"又唔係特別好着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:51:27.000Z","msg":"個牌子又柒"},{"pid":"e0d02c812ef1560c673214cdc295a5e4530baf9e","tid":2078842,"uid":60665,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:51:30.000Z","msg":"目娱乐节今日"},{"pid":"2d54b97e62a9fd499bf05c36cd73d769067945ab","tid":2078842,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:52:12.000Z","msg":"唔岩香港天氣著<br />\n<br />\n件衫d料鬼咁厚"},{"pid":"0c69c1b7495b0dca7b9926042606cbdfcfc9d1bd","tid":2078842,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e0d02c812ef1560c673214cdc295a5e4530baf9e","tid":2078842,"uid":60665,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:51:30.000Z","msg":"目娱乐节今日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T1